description.text: One person killed in Condorcanqui. At least 17 people injured, more than 5,689 buildings damaged or destroyed, several roads damaged and landslides and power outages occurred mostly in Amazonas, Cajamarca, Loreto and San Martin. Some buildings damaged in Loja, Ecuador.
